That was such a beautiful and enjoyable video mates! The cooking part made me laugh so hard :)
We have Winter here is Switzerland and i love it but in Januar /Februar and always feel some low Winter mood from the lack of Sun and outdoor sport.
You guys are Legends and i wish you and every other person out there right now ( especially firefighters and helpers) a good day and stay safe.

And now i go and walk with my Sleed dogs and hopefully can make some nice pictures and having a good time :)
Cheers guys
